You need to have a uPort app and get a key to make it run.
https://developer.uport.me/overview.html

I've updated the readme.

Hi Eric,
Thanks for the help. I have gotten this far maybe you'd be willing to give
me another hint.

If look at the http://localhost:3000/ get asked for Provider ? Blank page.

Got uPort mobile and app registered created the key.json as per your
instructions.

Went into truffle development from the /src dir, run migrate, get deployed
address for FeelGood, edit init_contract.js to use the deployed address in
the  first three const entities.
